1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
In 1905, a 26-year-old patent clerk, whose thesis had just been rejected,

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:07,440
sat at his desk stamping paperwork.

3
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:11,920
And in his spare time that year, he proved atoms are real, explained light,

4
00:00:11,920 --> 00:00:13,760
and rewrote space and time.

5
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:18,480
One man, one year, a side project.

6
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:21,840
So here's the question nobody can answer.

7
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,360
Why does nobody do that anymore?
